        "management": "Empiric IV antibiotics (ceftriaxone + gentamicin, or piperacillin-tazobactam) initially if severe/septic. Oral fluoroquinolones (ciprofloxacin 500 mg BID or levofloxacin 750 mg) for 4 weeks when stable. Alpha-blockers for voiding symptoms. Avoid vigorous DRE. Supportive: NSAIDs, hydration, bed rest."
