        ],
        "management": "Prolonged antibiotics (4-12 weeks): fluoroquinolones (levofloxacin 750 mg) or TMP-SMX. Alpha-blockers. NSAIDs. Repeat cultures. Surgical resection (TURP) if refractory and with prostatic calculi."
