        ],
        "management": "Multimodal: alpha-blockers, NSAIDs, physical therapy (pelvic floor), antidepressants (amitriptyline), gabapentinoids (pregabalin), psychological support. Avoid prolonged antibiotics. Phytotherapy (quercetin, saw palmetto). Lifestyle modifications."
